---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: false
description: "SYNTHERION is a synthwave bullet-hell shooter where every weapon is a loop and every run is a song. Built in Godot."
---

{% include "partials/hero.njk" %}

<main>

<section id="pitch" class="section section--pitch">
  <p class="pitch">
    The sprawl and depth of <em>Elite Dangerous</em>, compressed into 2D —
    built as a love letter to synthwave and darksynth.
  </p>
  <ul class="features">
    <li>
      <h3>Beat-Synced Weapons</h3>
      <p>Every gun fires on a beat division. Stack loadouts to compose your own arrangement mid-fight — every run becomes a track.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>A Galaxy in 2D</h3>
      <p>Deep ship systems, factions, and combat economies. The reach of a space sim, rendered in neon pixels.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Four-Player Co-op</h3>
      <p>Online. Bring a wingman, double the loops.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <h3>Soundtrack</h3>
      <p>A full analog-flavored score in the synthwave and darksynth tradition — with room for guest tracks from the scene.</p>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <aside class="artist-call">
    <h3 class="artist-call__title">Synthwave &amp; darksynth artists</h3>
    <p class="artist-call__body">
      If you make music in the scene, I'd love to put your tracks in the game. The plan is to wire
      them straight into drop tables and the soundtrack, so players can literally loot songs mid-run.
      <a href="{{ site.social.discordInvite }}" rel="noopener">Come say hi on Discord →</a>
    </p>
  </aside>
</section>

{% if collections.posts | length %}
<section class="section section--latest">
  <h2 class="section__heading">Latest Transmissions</h2>
  <div class="post-grid post-grid--latest">
    {% for post in collections.posts | limit(3) %}
      {% set post = post %}
      <div class="post-grid__item">
        {% include "partials/post-card.njk" %}
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  <div class="section__more">
    <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/devlog/">→ All transmissions</a>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% include "partials/trailer.njk" %}

</main>
